    <h2 class="title is-3">Who can join</h2>
    <p class="mb-3">The Amherst Community Band welcomes musicians of all abilities and ages, from enthusiastic amateurs to professionals, music teachers, middle and high school students, college students, and retirees.</p>
    <p>Membership is open to all who are interested and no audition is required.</p>
